    Overview

    Improve your writing with proofreading, summarization, autocompletion, rephrasing, AI chat assistance, and more.

    Enhance your writing using features like proofreading, autocompletion, rephrasing, translation, AI-powered chat support, and many more. Grazie is a free AI writing assistant that provides you with the essential tools you need to improve your writing across the web, from Google Docs to email and social media. Key features: Instant proofreading. AI-powered autocomplete suggestions. Context-aware AI chat. Effective rephrasing. Powerful tone detection. Immediate tone and style adjustment. Accurate summaries. Full support for all available features in both English and German. Customizable settings to suit your writing style. Get started Install the free Grazie extension in Chrome. Sign in using your JetBrains Account (or Google/Apple ID). Pin it to your toolbar for easy access to settings and AI chat. Grazie is a tool for everyone: Students: Present your next essay with flawless grammar and greater confidence. Academics: Prioritize research and critical thinking over extensive proofreading. Customer support: Craft clear, concise, and professional responses. Content creators: Overcome writer's block and generate new ideas. Office workers: Master your inbox and send clear and impactful emails and messages. Private use: Spend less time responding and more time living. FAQs Which web applications are supported by Grazie? Grazie works with Google Docs, Gmail, Slack (Web), Confluence, and many more. How many languages does Grazie support? Instant proofreading is available for English, German, Russian, and Ukrainian. Translation is supported for English, German, French, Spanish, Russian, Korean, Chinese, Japanese and Dutch. AI-powered features such as Summarize, Translate, Improve, Change tone, and Paraphrase are available in English and German. How safe is Grazie? Grazie adheres to strict measures to protect the privacy and security of user data. We dont use your content to train models, either our own or those of third parties. None of your text is retained in the memory or logs of our servers. Find more information in the Grazie Terms of Service (https://www.jetbrains.com/legal/docs/terms/grazie/) and the JetBrains Privacy Policy (https://www.jetbrains.com/legal/docs/privacy/privacy/). Is Grazie available in my region? Access to Grazie is available only in the territories where our AI service providers are active. Please check the full list of territories here: https://www.jetbrains.com/legal/docs/terms/jetbrains-ai/service-territory/.
